  "prompt": "Why do girls wear sports bras?",
  "response": "Girls and women wear sports bras for a variety of reasons related to comfort, support, and performance during physical activity:\n\n*   **Support:** Sports bras are designed to minimize breast movement during exercise. This is important because excessive movement can cause discomfort, pain, and even long-term sagging.\n\n*   **Comfort:** By reducing bounce and providing a snug fit, sports bras can make exercise more comfortable. They also help to prevent chafing and irritation.\n\n*   **Performance:** Some athletes find that wearing a sports bra improves their performance by allowing them to focus on their workout without being distracted by breast movement.\n\n*   **Moisture-wicking:** Many sports bras are made from moisture-wicking fabrics that help to keep the wearer cool and dry during exercise.",
